  <section class="flex flex-col p-12 md:py-32 md:px-60 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row text-start">
      <h2 class="text-5xl mb-8 w-full md:w-1/2">uECO Energy-saving Mode</h2>
      <p
        class="w-full md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-12 md:text-2xl text-gray-600 md:pr-20"
      >
        With the uECO mode, energy consumption of the scanner is reduced by
        partially powering down system components while maintaining the basic
        functionalities to ensure that the system can quickly resume work. This
        significantly improves energy efficiency, thereby reducing the overall
        environmental impact and operating costs.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10">
      <div
        class="flex-1 p-16 text-gray-200"
        style="background-image: url('/public/images/products/CT/uCT550/map1.webp');"
      >
        <div class="slide-title-part text-xl mb-8">01</div>
        <div class="slide-title-main text-2xl pb-4 border-b mb-4">
          <p>Reduce Electricity Consumption</p>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-content text-lg">
          Reduce electricity consumption for operation and ambient cooling by up
          to 31.4% compared to conventional stand-by mode.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex-1 p-16 text-gray-200"
        style="background-image: url('/public/images/products/CT/uCT550/map1.webp');"
      >
        <div class="slide-title-part text-xl mb-8">02</div>
        <div class="slide-title-main text-2xl pb-4 border-b mb-4">
          <p>One-click for uECO</p>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-content text-lg">
          During the system idle time, such as at nights or on weekends, the
          system can switch to the uECO mode with one-click.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex-1 p-16 text-gray-200"
        style="background-image: url('/public/images/products/CT/uCT550/map1.webp');"
      >
