        <div class="slide-title-main text-2xl pb-4 border-b mb-4">
          <p>Smart Wake-up</p>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-content text-lg">
          Upon waking up from the uECO mode, the system is able to quickly
          become stable and ready for work, thus reducing the wait time while
          providing consistent high-quality images.
